# YouTube Desktop App ğŸ¬

A sleek desktop YouTube wrapper built with Electron.js that bypasses DNS-level restrictions and provides a native app experience.

â“ Why I Made This
YouTube isnâ€™t available as a native app on the Windows store. I use DNS filters for privacy/safety, but they restrict YouTube when applied to the browser. So I made this app using Electron to run YouTube as its own standalone desktop experience â€” DNS-free, smooth, and silent.

