## ğŸ”§ Configuration

### DNS Settings
The app uses Cloudflare's DNS-over-HTTPS by default. You can modify the DNS servers in `main.js`:

```javascript
app.commandLine.appendSwitch('dns-over-https-servers', 'https://your-dns-server.com/dns-query');
```

### Window Customization
Adjust window properties in `main.js`:

```javascript
const mainWindow = new BrowserWindow({
  width: 1200,        // Adjust width
  height: 800,        // Adjust height
  title: "YouTube",   // Window title
  // ... other options
});
```

## ğŸ› Troubleshooting

### Common Issues

**App doesn't start silently**
- Try using `YouTube.vbs` instead of `start.bat`
- Ensure Node.js is properly installed and in PATH

**Login issues**
- Clear browser cache and cookies
- Try logging in through your default browser first

**DNS blocking still active**
- Check if your DNS provider blocks DoH requests
- Try changing DNS servers in the configuration

